message.content:
On Facebook, to delete a photo or video from your story, follow these steps:

1. Open the Facebook app on your phone.
2. Tap the "Your Story" icon at the top of your News Feed (it should show your profile picture with a blue circle around it).
3. Find the photo or video you want to delete and tap it to view it in full screen.
4. In the bottom-right corner of the screen, tap More (the three-dot icon) and then tap "Delete Photo" or "Delete Video."
5. A prompt will appear asking if you are sure that you want to delete this post from your story; confirm by tapping Delete.

This will remove only that particular photo/video from Your Story section while keeping other content within intact
